# ILOs for this week

MAKE SHORT LECTURE ON DEPRESSION AND WATCH AS PART OF WEEK 1
INSTEAD, THIS WEEK BECOMES ABOUT DESIGNING WOMEN'S MH RESEARCH - DESIGN STUDY IN GROUPS, PRESENT TO PPI GROUP - OR - 2 GROUPS FOR 2 QUESTIONS, SUBGROUPS ARE DIFFERENT DISCIPLINES (BIOLOGISTS, PSYCHOLOGISTS, SOCIAL SCIENTISTS, HEALTH ECONOMISTS, LAY PEOPLE IE PPI - ILLUSTRATE IMPORTANCE AND CHALLENGES OF INTERDISCIPLINARY RESEARCH AND ENGAGEMENT)

- Describe subtypes of depression
- Are we pathologising normal sadness (grief) 
- Epidemiology (genetic epi?)
- Clinical assessments of depression
- Courses and consequences of depression 
- Causes + diathesis stress
- Inflammation and immune system *** Physiology
- Parenting and depression **** Perinatal
- Differences in male and female experiences of depression *** Week 1

